</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">豆腐のカニあんかけ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<abstract>
<sentence>つまり、カニ缶入りトロ〜リ湯豆腐って感じ！</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</abstract>
<titleBlock>
<title>
